通，證明電話網絡運作正常，只是不能報警。延至下午1時許，情況仍然持續。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向警察公共關係科了解情況，有待回應。"},{"pid":"46fbbc1208156053f1189571447c159ae8073c67","tid":822174,"uid":53901,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d5d77509c746105ee26b896a57193545cf8311f","tid":822174,"uid":17510,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"本網記者今日中午12時許嘗試致電「999」報警求助，惟電話多次未能接通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞啲記者係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地都話太多人打唔通   你仲要加多腳落去<br />\n真正有需要既人就因為你jam左條線面打唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因寓所受颱風破壞，本網記者今日中午12時許嘗試致電「999」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de90419ccf40be77a276da78c203f74038debcc","tid":822174,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46fbbc1208156053f1189571447c159ae8073c67","tid":822174,"uid":53901,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d5d77509c746105ee26b896a57193545cf8311f","tid":822174,"uid":17510,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"本網記者今日中午12時許嘗試致電「999」報警求助，惟電話多次未能接通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞啲記者係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地都話太多人打唔通   你仲要加多腳落去<br />\n真正有需要既人就因為你jam左條線面打唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因寓所受颱風破壞，本網記者今日中午12時許嘗試致電「999」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:44:34.000Z","msg":"打風爆左玻璃所以要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左住係木屋寮屋之外  我真係好有興趣睇下位記者間屋有咩咁緊急要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c96abcfd695f43bf0ac6ed7c2e32b268bdb20e5","tid":822174,"uid":53901,"like":0,"dislike":0